---
title: Dill-Garlic Salmon Salad with Ranch Dressing and DIY Croutons
description: This dish makes it easy to build up everyone's plate with what they love! Little one doesn't like croutons or tomatoes? No problem, keep them all to yourself. Everyone loves ranch – drizzle it over everything and this dinner will be a hit!
